Package org.forgerock.opendj.server.config.server

Interface HTTPOauth2TokenIntrospectionAuthorizationMechanismCfg

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Configuration, HTTPAuthorizationMechanismCfg, HTTPOauth2AuthorizationMechanismCfg
    public interface HTTPOauth2TokenIntrospectionAuthorizationMechanismCfg
extends HTTPOauth2AuthorizationMechanismCfg
    A server-side interface for querying HTTP Oauth2 Token Introspection Authorization Mechanism settings.

    The HTTP Oauth2 Token Introspection Authorization Mechanism is used to define OAuth2 authorization using an introspection (RFC7662) compliant authorization server.
